node.contents: In an Adobe AIR application compiled for Android I am getting ANR errors with the cause keyDispatchingTimedOut. The workflow is as follows:

astNode.text: In an Adobe AIR application compiled for Android I am getting ANR errors with the cause keyDispatchingTimedOut. The workflow is as follows:

node.contents:
1. Sounds are playing, an embedded SWF is playing.
  2. User presses a button - sounds/SWF stop playing
  3. Application waits 3 seconds
  4. Application makes some asynchronous calls to a server
  5. Application handles the result, and pushes a new view to the viewstack.
  6. New view appears
  7. Between 5-10% of the time, after a few seconds, the ANR occurs.
